mx.org.pescadormvp.core.shared

Class PescadorMVPLocale

  • java.lang.Object
    • mx.org.pescadormvp.core.shared.PescadorMVPLocale
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IsSerializable, Serializable

    public class PescadorMVPLocale
extends Object
implements Serializable, IsSerializable

    A class that holds a localeName (as used in URLs or locale cookies) and a localized (display) name for that locale.

    Here hashCode() and equals(java.lang.Object) only take into account localeName, and not the display name.
